txt.en: You have defeated many Jangovar Marauders in the wilds near Dale. Your efforts will ensure the safety of all those within the town's walls.
Jangovar Marauders, lurking in the wilds, encroach upon the city of Dale. These marauders should be dealt with swiftly.
Jangovar Marauders can be found in the wilds near the city of Dale in the Dale-lands.\n\nYou should defeat any Jangovar Marauders you come across.
Jangovar Marauders encroach upon the city of Dale and should be dealt with swiftly.
